OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,FGranada Reports correspondent Paul
OL,7,FCrone spoke to Carole about her father
OL,8,Fand uncle.
OL,10,FThe daughter of a soldier killed on D-
OL,11,FDay says her father and his brother
OL,12,Fwere 'still together' even when they
OL,13,Fdied.
OL,15,FColour Sergeant Norman Davis was
OL,16,Fkilled just 10 miles east of
OL,17,FLieutenant Alan Davis - making them
OL,18,Fthe only British brothers to die on
OL,19,Fthe Normandy beaches on the same day.
