OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,F"One of the soldiers told my mother
OL,7,Fthat they were nearly on the ship
OL,8,Freturning after he had done the job he
OL,9,Fwas supposed to be doing," said Carole.
OL,11,F"He looked back to see where his
OL,12,Ffriend was and he saw he was injured
OL,13,Fso he went back to help him bring him
OL,14,Fto the ship and that's when he was
OL,15,Fkilled."
OL,17,FBoth brothers died that day, with
OL,18,Ftheir mother receiving telegrams to
OL,19,Fannounce their deaths on the same day.
