OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,FCarole continued: "I'm not sure which
OL,7,Fone she got first, to say one of her
OL,8,Fsons has died.
OL,10,F"In the afternoon, she got the second
OL,11,Ftelegram, to say the second son had
OL,12,Fdied and apparently, that caused her
OL,13,Fhair to go white overnight with the
OL,14,Fshock."
OL,16,FThough Carole was only two-years-old
OL,17,Fwhen her father died, her mother tells
OL,18,Fher a story of her speaking to him
OL,19,Fafter his passing.
