OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,F"They did everything together more or
OL,7,Fless, even joining the first job and
OL,8,Flisting together, they were always
OL,9,Ftogether," added Carole.
OL,11,F"They married at similar times even
OL,12,Fthough there was three years between
OL,13,Fthem, and to find that they were in
OL,14,Fthe same area was terrific really...it
OL,15,Fjust followed through somehow.
OL,17,F"Even the telegrams coming on the same
OL,18,Fday, they were still together."
