OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,FCarole said her most prized
OL,7,Fpossessions are her father's medals
OL,8,Fand a letter written by her father's
OL,9,Fcommanding officer shortly after D-
OL,10,FDay. She only discovered the letter a
OL,11,Fyear ago.
OL,13,FThe letter said: "I found his body
OL,14,Flater and he was not marked in anyway,
OL,15,Fhe has been buried in a peaceful quiet
OL,16,Ffield with his comrades."
