OL,3,CThe only British brothers to die on
OL,4,Cthe beaches of Normandy
OL,6,FStephen Benson from the Cheshire Roll
OL,7,Fof Honour, said: "History is an
OL,8,Fimportant element of learning if we
OL,9,Funderstand our history and we learn
OL,10,Ffrom our history we can the future
OL,11,Fbetter."
OL,13,F"I like to believe that story that he
OL,14,Fdid come and talk to me when he died
OL,15,Fbecause that was a chance for him to
OL,16,Fsee me, that's comforting," said
OL,17,FCarole.
OL,19,F"I've always missed having a father,
OL,20,Falways."
